        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For Brisbane businesses, a power outage is more than an inconvenience; it represents a significant risk to operational continuity and site safety. Regular maintenance ensures that your standby power systems are ready to engage immediately when the local grid fails, particularly during the humid summer months. By identifying minor mechanical issues before they escalate, you can avoid the high costs associated with emergency repairs and unexpected downtime."
