      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "When local infrastructure fails during the storm season, having a rapid response plan is critical for Brisbane business continuity. Emergency generator support provides the peace of mind that technical help is available to restore power when every minute of downtime impacts your bottom line. It is essential to have a service partner who understands the local geography and can provide prompt on-site assistance regardless of the conditions."
