      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Professional servicing involves more than just a cursory check; it requires a comprehensive assessment of both mechanical and electrical components. GenFix provides tailored maintenance schedules designed to meet the unique demands of Brisbane's commercial sector, from retail hubs to industrial manufacturing plants. A thorough service history not only maintains the manufacturer's warranty but also provides data that can predict when components may need proactive replacement."
